00:16:49,554 --> 00:16:52,554
It's not yogurt.
It's mayonnaise.

246
00:16:52,594 --> 00:16:54,554
Oh, right.
There we are then.

247
00:16:54,634 --> 00:16:56,354
Mm.

248
00:16:56,434 --> 00:16:59,194
On for a videofest tonight?

249
00:17:00,554 --> 00:17:03,594
I got some absolute classics.

