00:17:06,035 --> 00:17:08,955
- Smile.
- No.

251
00:17:12,195 --> 00:17:16,235
- Smile.
- I've got nothing to smile about.

252
00:17:24,915 --> 00:17:26,795
Okay.

253
00:17:26,835 --> 00:17:29,355
In about seven seconds,

254
00:17:29,435 --> 00:17:32,035
