to marry me.

255
00:17:38,436 --> 00:17:40,916
[ Spike ]
Imagine.

256
00:17:40,996 --> 00:17:45,596
Somewhere in the world
there's a man who's allowed to kiss her.

257
00:17:45,676 --> 00:17:47,996
[ Both Laughing ]

258
00:17:48,076 --> 00:17:50,676
Yes, she is, uh,

259
00:17:50,756 --> 00:17:54,396
fairly fabulous.

260
00:18:02,196 --> 00:18:04,637
