470
00:31:48,265 --> 00:31:49,745
Hi.

471
00:31:51,826 --> 00:31:53,706
Hi.

472
00:31:53,746 --> 00:31:57,306
Um-- Yeah, so the, um--

473
00:31:57,386 --> 00:32:01,466
the-- the thing I was doing tonight,
