00:32:01,546 --> 00:32:03,946
I told them I had
to spend the evening...

475
00:32:03,986 --> 00:32:07,666
with Britain's premier
equestrian journalist.

476
00:32:07,706 --> 00:32:10,666
Oh. Well, great.

477
00:32:10,746 --> 00:32:12,866
Fantastic.
That's, uh--

